net.smartcosmos.model.integration

Interface INotificationEndpoint

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAccountContext, IDomainResource<INotificationEndpoint>, IMinimalReferentialObject, IMoniker, INamedObject<INotificationEndpoint>, IReferentialObject, IUrnNamespace
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NotificationEndpoint

    public interface INotificationEndpoint
extends INamedObject<INotificationEndpoint>, IReferentialObject
    Defines a single external integration endpoint whereby the platform will issue an HTTP/S POST of events occurring within a given account context in near real-time.
